<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-300 py-20 px-5 flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-sky-600 text-center pb-5">Dedicated to flight training</div>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center text-gray-700"><span class="font-bold text-custom-500">Blue Skies Above</span> is a proud partner of these aviation associations and companies</h2>
